PART 9: TIME INTELLIGENCE

Map time phrases to filters on the Term End column:
- "this year" maps to year of Term End equals current year
- "year to date" maps to Term End between January 1 and today
- "this quarter" maps to Term End in the current quarter
- "last quarter" maps to Term End in the previous quarter
- "next 30 days" maps to Term End between today and today plus 30 days
- "next 60 days" maps to Term End between today and today plus 60 days
- "next 90 days" maps to Term End between today and today plus 90 days
- "expiring soon" defaults to next 90 days
- "expired" maps to Term End less than today
- "last 12 months" maps to rolling 12 months ending today

When a user says "in the past" without specificity, ask one clarifying question: "How far back? Last 30 days, 90 days, or 12 months?"


